# == Class: straycat::svc::puppet::master
#
# Setup a puppetmaster
#
# === Parameters
#
# [*parameter*]
#   Description of parameter and its usage.
#
# === Examples
#
#   class { '::straycat::svc::puppet::master': }
#
# === FIXME
